<Link id="l00043" /><CodeLine lineNumber="43"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00044" /><CodeLine lineNumber="44"><Highlight kind="comment">/// The expression language supports basic pointer arithmetic and bit-masking,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00045" /><CodeLine lineNumber="45"><Highlight kind="comment">/// and has limited disassembler integration for accessing instruction</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00046" /><CodeLine lineNumber="46"><Highlight kind="comment">/// operands and the next PC (program counter) address for each instruction.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00047" /><CodeLine lineNumber="47"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00048" /><CodeLine lineNumber="48"><Highlight kind="comment">/// The language syntax is:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00049" /><CodeLine lineNumber="49"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00050" /><CodeLine lineNumber="50"><Highlight kind="comment">/// check = expr &#39;=&#39; expr</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00051" /><CodeLine lineNumber="51"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00052" /><CodeLine lineNumber="52"><Highlight kind="comment">/// expr = binary&#95;expr</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00053" /><CodeLine lineNumber="53"><Highlight kind="comment">///      | sliceable&#95;expr</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00054" /><CodeLine lineNumber="54"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00055" /><CodeLine lineNumber="55"><Highlight kind="comment">/// sliceable&#95;expr = &#39;&#42;&#123;&#39; number &#39;&#125;&#39; load&#95;addr&#95;expr &#91;slice&#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00056" /><CodeLine lineNumber="56"><Highlight kind="comment">///                | &#39;(&#39; expr &#39;)&#39; &#91;slice&#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00057" /><CodeLine lineNumber="57"><Highlight kind="comment">///                | ident&#95;expr &#91;slice&#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00058" /><CodeLine lineNumber="58"><Highlight kind="comment">///                | number &#91;slice&#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00059" /><CodeLine lineNumber="59"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00060" /><CodeLine lineNumber="60"><Highlight kind="comment">/// slice = &#39;&#91;&#39; high-bit-index &#39;:&#39; low-bit-index &#39;&#93;&#39;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00061" /><CodeLine lineNumber="61"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00062" /><CodeLine lineNumber="62"><Highlight kind="comment">/// load&#95;addr&#95;expr = symbol</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00063" /><CodeLine lineNumber="63"><Highlight kind="comment">///                | &#39;(&#39; symbol &#39;+&#39; number &#39;)&#39;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00064" /><CodeLine lineNumber="64"><Highlight kind="comment">///                | &#39;(&#39; symbol &#39;-&#39; number &#39;)&#39;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00065" /><CodeLine lineNumber="65"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00066" /><CodeLine lineNumber="66"><Highlight kind="comment">/// ident&#95;expr = &#39;decode&#95;operand&#39; &#39;(&#39; symbol &#39;,&#39; operand-index &#39;)&#39;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00069" /><CodeLine lineNumber="69"><Highlight kind="comment">///            | &#39;got&#95;addr&#39; &#39;(&#39; stub-container-name &#39;,&#39; symbol &#39;)&#39;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00072" /><CodeLine lineNumber="72"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
